⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Dying Future
node LMZ · LMZ · ⟦The Dying Future:LMZ:1cd5f9⟧

WHO   — The Dying Future — the world that reached back
WHAT  — The reason for everything: a future desperate enough to gamble its salvation on whether two children would listen to a rabbit.
WHERE — LMZ · The Last Mimzy (2007)  Framework inputs: The Last Mimzy (2007, dir. Robert Shaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the gentle wonder rests on a grave premise — that we may yet poison ourselves, and need our own innocence to come back.
HOW   — By reaching across time with a box of toys, betting everything on the kindness and curiosity of the past.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  We poisoned ourselves, and we had one idea left: send toys to the children of the past, and pray they would listen. They did.

